{
  "texts": [
    "Thus, it is essential to examine this phenomenon critically, acknowledging that current power relationships, the commodification of science, and the \"publish or perish\" culture in science and scientific authorship are integral parts of the problem.",
    "Viewing ChatGPT or other LLMs as a challenge is beneficial only if we consider how autopoietic systems function.",
    "Specifically, if the scientific system's paradigm prioritizes quantity as a standard, then new technology will be observed and autopoieticaly adapted accordingly.",
    "Accordingly, the technology of generative AI right now is only a piece in a puzzle.",
    "This is also a reason why human-centric solutions which focus on the individual scientists breaching moral and ethical presumption alone are not sufficient."
  ]
}